issue.title: New directory page layout
issue.body:
Updates the repository and directory page to show the following information:
* README file if there exists one in the directory
* Linear file browser, showing diff stats over the past month
* Recent commits
* Recent contributors

Removes:
* The commits and contributors menu items from the repository page. These are still accessible by clicking the headers in the commits and contributors panel
